1. Building zync-gui
--------------------
In order to build the zync-gui application all one should have to do is the
following command under their user account (This should be from the root of
the project directory):

$ make

2. Installing zync-gui
----------------------
To install zync-gui all one must do is the following command as root (from the
root of the projects directory).

# make install

4. Using zync-gui
-----------------
Simply execute the zync-gui command as follows.

$ zync-gui